general.description: The Zee 2 Is The Best Residential Mower In Its Class With Big Engines, Big Decks, And Big Value. No Other Residential Mower Gives You More Muscle For Your Money.

features: The Mower With More Muscle For Your Money.
Protects Fuel Tank From Sun And Impact Damage.
Greaseable And Lifetime Warranty Against Breakage.
Formed And Welded 10 Ga Deck Shell.
A 23 Horsepower Engine From Kawasaki® Or Kohler® To Power You At Up To 3.1 Acres Per Hour.
Allows You To Quickly Raise The Deck To Avoid Objects And Locks The Deck In Travel Height For Transporting And Storing.
options: **Acres Per Hour Is Calculated On 80% Operator Accuracy And Mowing Conditions With An Optimum Cutting Height Of 2.5 To 4.5 Inches.
